results.shortDescription: One heart is an upcoming documentary picture describing about true internal feelings of the band
results.longDescription: One Heart is a concert film featuring 15 most-loved and popular songs by A. R. Rahman. The film is punctuated by unseen personal clips and a series of in-depth interview with A. R. Rahman who share with us his thoughts about performing on stage, how he came to choose the band that toured with him in 14 cities in America and the humility he feels when armies of his fans shower love on him. Through his performance, AR brings the arena alive, evoking old memories and exciting his fans across generations.
